ygData.messageBody:
If you can't find onyx in Freeport (sorry I don't know yet all that's
available) Felwithe is a much easier trip than Erudin (or anywhere's
west). You take the boat to butcherblock, run through that zone, then a
short fun in greater feydark and you are at Felwithe.

-----Original Message-----
From: DeGirolami, Franck [mailto:degirolami@...]
Sent: Wednesday, April 28, 1999 2:03 PM
To: Eqenchanters (E-mail)
Subject: [eqenchanters] Onyx in Freeport


From: "DeGirolami, Franck" <degirolami@...>

ok I've been working on my jewelry skill last night and I'm just done
maxing
it out with bloodstone ( skill 26 ). the next stone to work with from
what I
read is Onyx but I cant find it in Freeport. so maybe I should jump
directly

jump

tiny

find
onyx?
Thanks.
Skara.
